'''Aggwa''' neɣ '''Aylal''' d irem i yettwanefken i yal iyunen yettemcabin deg iylanen yettwaberzen kan s unect n tmerniwt neɣ n tdersi n tesmekta. S umata, aggwa isgensis-d tehri neɣ aɣawas i tneẓẓi i uzenzar (izenzaren izelɣanen, [[Afutun|ifutunen]], [[imesli]]) am umḍafar n tesmekta, neɣ [[tasmekta n umussu]] neɣ [[teɣzi n tamdeswelt]] neɣ [[asnagar]] neɣ jean tesmekta niḍen yettaken assaɣ. Amedya, aggwa n [[tazelɣa β|tzelɣiwin n bita]] isgensis-d aẓuni (afraq) n [[tafasa tasintant|tfasa tasintant]] [[aliktṛun|taliktṛunant]] tibawt n waggay i d-ittfɣen s uwurman seg [[Nuklid|yinukliden]] [[Aṛadyurmid|urmiden n izenzaren]].

Mi ara ad yeglu kra n [[Aṛadyurmid|uferdis aṛadyurmid]] s [[tazelɣa α|tzelɣiwin nAlfa]], ad fersent aggwa seg tzelɣiwin n Alfa ilan yiwet n [[tafasa|tfasa]] neɣ ugar.

